categories: Category:Unidentified Jedi of the Jedi Order

nodes.text: A female Togruta Jedi lived at some point during Galactic History.

This character was depicted on the "Mystical Energies" card of the The Nightsister's Revenge, the base set of the Star Wars Galaxies Trading Card Game, which was illustrated by artist John Stanko. Most cards of the game depict the events of the Galactic Civil War. Therefore, it is impossible to determine the time period this Jedi lived in without additional information.
